description: If you know your way to San Jose, you might as well know your way directly to Agha’s Gyros Express because next time you need some pita, this is the truck for you. You get Manhattan-caliber mediterranean street food without the attitude. In fact, everyone raves about the friendly customer service they’re serving here almost as much as the fantastic food!The menu is 100% Halal and offers rich, juicy chicken and tender, tasty lamb that you can enjoy either over a generous portion of savory, flavorful rice or wrapped in a soft, pillowy pita- all at prices, speed, and quality that remind you of why you love food trucks to begin with. Come out and enjoy this delicious fare, introduce yourself to these gyro heroes, and express your love for Agha’s Gyros.
name: Agha's Gyros Express
